+# Data Broker Read API
+
+All endpoints are mounted under `/api` and return JSON responses.
+
+## User Data Endpoints
+
+### GET /api/user/:userId/default-league-season
+
+Returns the default league and season for a user based on their league interests and upcoming schedule.
+
+**Path Parameters:**
+- `userId` (string) - The user ID
+
+**Response:**
+```json
+{ "league_id": 6555, "season_id": 99410 }
+```
+
+---
+
+### GET /api/user/:userId/features
+
+Returns the list of enabled feature names for a user.
+
+**Path Parameters:**
+- `userId` (string) - The user ID
+
+**Response:**
+```json
+["feature_a", "feature_b"]
+```
+
+---
+
+### GET /api/user/:userId/ir-link-state
+
+Returns the iRacing account link status for a user.
+
+**Path Parameters:**
+- `userId` (string) - The user ID
+
+**Response:**
+```json
+{ "isVerified": true, "irCustId": "12345", "msgSent": false }
+```
+
+---
+
+### GET /api/user/:userId/leagues
+
+Returns the leagues a user has expressed interest in.
+
+**Path Parameters:**
+- `userId` (string) - The user ID
+
+**Response:**
+```json
+[{ "name": "League Name", "league_id": 6555, "short_name": "LN" }]
+```
+
+---
+
+### GET /api/user/:userId/context
+
+Resolves the default league/season/subsession context for a user. Falls back through increasingly broad resolution when specific params are invalid.
+
+**Path Parameters:**
+- `userId` (string) - The user ID
+
+**Query Parameters (all optional):**
+- `league` (string) - League ID to resolve context for
+- `season` (string) - Season ID to resolve context for
+- `subsession` (string) - Subsession ID to resolve context for
+
+**Response:**
+```json
+{ "league_id": 6555, "season_id": 99410, "subsession_id": 12345 }
+```
+
+---
+
+## Config Endpoints
+
+### GET /api/config/leagues/:leagueId/teams
+
+Returns teams and members for all seasons in a league.
+
+**Path Parameters:**
+- `leagueId` (string) - The league ID
+
+**Response:**
+```json
+{
+  "leageu_id": 6555,
+  "seasons": [
+    {
+      "season_id": 99410,
+      "teams": [
+        { "team_name": "Alpha Racing", "team_id": 1, "team_members": [111, 222] }
+      ]
+    }
+  ]
+}
+```
+
+---
+
+### GET /api/config/active-league-schedule
+
+Returns the schedule for all active leagues and their seasons.
+
+**Response:**
+```json
+{
+  "leagues": [
+    {
+      "league_id": 6555,
+      "name": "League Name",
+      "seasons": [
+        {
+          "season_id": 99410,
+          "car_id": 77,
+          "comment": "Season Name",
+          "events": [
+            { "event_id": 1, "time": "2025-03-15T20:00:00Z", "track_id": 123, "comment": "Event Name" }
+          ]
+        }
+      ]
+    }
+  ]
+}
+```
+
+---
+
+### GET /api/config/tracks
+
+Returns display information for all tracks.
+
+**Response:**
+```json
+{
+  "123": { "display": "Daytona International Speedway", "short_display": "Daytona" }
+}
+```
+
+---
+
+### GET /api/config/context
+
+Resolves the default league/season/subsession context (without user-specific league interests).
+
+**Query Parameters (all optional):**
+- `league` (string) - League ID
+- `season` (string) - Season ID
+- `subsession` (string) - Subsession ID
+
+**Response:**
+```json
+{ "league_id": 6555, "season_id": 99410, "subsession_id": 12345 }
+```
+
+---
+
+## Publication Endpoints
+
+### GET /api/publications/:subsessionId/status
+
+Checks whether a subsession has been published.
+
+**Path Parameters:**
+- `subsessionId` (number) - The subsession ID
+
+**Response:**
+```json
+{ "subsession_id": 12345, "published": true }
+```
+
+**Errors:**
+- `400` - Invalid subsession ID (non-numeric)
+
+---
+
+## Channel Endpoints
+
+### GET /api/channels/:channelId/users
+
+Returns a mapping of display names to Discord user mentions for a channel's guild (based on recent message activity).
+
+**Path Parameters:**
+- `channelId` (string) - The Discord channel ID
+
+**Response:**
+```json
+{ "John Doe": "<@123456>", "Jane Smith": "<@789012>" }
+```
+
+---
+
+## Data Lake Endpoints
+
+### GET /api/datalake/:namespace/:type
+
+Fetches a document from the external data lake.
+
+**Path Parameters:**
+- `namespace` (string) - Data namespace (e.g., `ldata-irweb`, `ldata-rsltsts`)
+- `type` (string) - Document type (e.g., `leagueSeasonSessions`, `leagueSeasons`, `membersData`, `leagueDriverStats`, `singleMemberData`)
+
+**Query Parameters (all optional):**
+- `league` - League ID
+- `season` - Season ID
+- `subsession` - Subsession ID
+- `simsession` - Sim session number
+- `driver` - Driver/customer ID
+- `car` - Car ID
+- `track` - Track ID
+- `sessionType` - Session type
+- `custId` - Customer ID
+
+**Response:** The raw JSON document from the data lake.
+
+**Errors:**
+- `404` - Document not found
